Body: Next Steps Updated: Waiting for customer to test again with the 5941 client.

What We've Learned Updated: Under content aware reports, the customer gets tens of thousands of redundant and excessive logs from temp outlook appdata files. They tried adding it as a file location in allowlist and selecting the computers to prevent it from popping up in logs, but to no avail. In addition, aside from seeing emails with destination details, they also see the exact replicates without destination details.
They tried to add the file location in multiple ways, but it didn't help.

Next Steps Updated: 23Jan: Will check back with customer in 2 weeks to see if email alerts are still received.

They tried to add the file location in multiple ways, but it didn't help.
